<p>I am trying to test <code>ClassA</code>, the test method calls a private method in this class, <code>privateA()</code>. The method <code>privateA()</code> calls class <code>ClassB</code>'s public method <code>publicB()</code>. </p>  <p>I would like to mock the value returned by the <code>publicB()</code> function using <code>when().thenReturn()</code>, but I get the following error: </p>  <blockquote>   <p>org.mockito.exceptions.misusing.InvalidUseOfMatchersException</p> </blockquote>